							<v8:lang>en</v8:lang>
							<v8:content>Business Entities created after August 13, 2009 budget scientific institutions in accordance with the Federal Law of August 23, 1996 N 127-FZ "On Science and State Scientific and Technical Policy" and educational institutions of higher professional education in accordance with the Federal Law of 22 August 1996 N 125-FZ "On higher and postgraduate professional education"</v8:content>
